    <letteral>O</letteral>, but it is easier on the reader to capitalize the whole syllable.</para>
    <para> <indexterm type="general"><primary>lerfu words</primary><secondary>table of Lojban</secondary></indexterm> Therefore, the following table represents the basic Lojban alphabet:</para>
